  <brief_title>Safety and Feasibility Study of Autologous Bone Marrow Cell Transplantation in Patients With Peripheral Arterial Occlusive Disease (PAOD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>(Intraarterial Progenitor Cell Transplantation of Bone Marrow Mononuclear Cells for Induction of Neovascularization in Patients With Peripheral Arterial Occlusive Disease)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
